# Keep these LF on every platform. core.autocrlf=true would otherwise check
# them out as CRLF on Windows, and chezmoi copies the source bytes verbatim
# into the target — a stray \r breaks the bash status line script and leaves a
# permanent CRLF-vs-LF chezmoi diff on the rendered settings.json.
*.sh        text eol=lf
*.sh.tmpl   text eol=lf
*.zsh       text eol=lf
*.json.tmpl text eol=lf
